### Notification Service API Tests

### 1. Send Email Notification - Registration
POST http://localhost:8087/api/v1/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "type": "REGISTRATION",
  "channel": "EMAIL",
  "recipient": "user@example.com",
  "subject": "Welcome to GaadiX",
  "message": "Thank you for registering with GaadiX. Your account has been created successfully."
}

### 2. Send SMS Notification - Verification
POST http://localhost:8087/api/v1/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "type": "VERIFICATION",
  "channel": "SMS",
  "recipient": "+919876543210",
  "subject": "Verification Code",
  "message": "Your GaadiX verification code is: 123456. Valid for 10 minutes."
}

### 3. Send Push Notification - Payment
POST http://localhost:8087/api/v1/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 2,
  "type": "PAYMENT",
  "channel": "PUSH",
  "recipient": "device_token_123",
  "subject": "Payment Successful",
  "message": "Your payment of ₹5,50,000 has been processed successfully."
}

### 4. Send Email - Booking Confirmation
POST http://localhost:8087/api/v1/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 3,
  "type": "BOOKING",
  "channel": "EMAIL",
  "recipient": "buyer@example.com",
  "subject": "Booking Confirmed",
  "message": "Your booking for Maruti Swift has been confirmed. Booking ID: BK12345"
}

### 5. Send SMS - Alert
POST http://localhost:8087/api/v1/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "type": "ALERT",
  "channel": "SMS",
  "recipient": "+919876543210",
  "subject": "Security Alert",
  "message": "New login detected from Mumbai. If this wasn't you, please secure your account."
}

### 6. Send Email - Promotional
POST http://localhost:8087/api/v1/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 4,
  "type": "PROMOTIONAL",
  "channel": "EMAIL",
  "recipient": "customer@example.com",
  "subject": "Special Offer - 10% Off",
  "message": "Get 10% off on your next car purchase. Use code: GAADIX10. Valid till 31st Dec."
}

### 7. Get User Notifications
GET http://localhost:8087/api/v1/notifications/user/1

### 8. Get Notification by ID
GET http://localhost:8087/api/v1/notifications/1
